      <scopecontent id="aspace_ef3e9e0d1decc42c1e3d24b0ea66195b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of minutes, correspondence, budgets, manuals, memoranda, and handbooks of the Yale Human Resouces Office. The records document personnel, committees, expenses, and labor unions.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_fc9f3092791c4ddb5e4de48ca55f75c3">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
